OL,7,FA fly tipper who was caught on CCTV
OL,8,Fdumping waste before it was set alight
OL,9,Fon an estate in Houghton Le Spring has
OL,10,Fbeen ordered to pay out almost #2,000.
OL,12,FDarren Roxby pleaded guilty to three
OL,13,Fcounts of fly-tipping at South
OL,14,FTyneside Magistrates Cour,t as well as
OL,15,Ftransporting controlled waste in the
OL,16,Fcourse of a business or otherwise,
OL,17,Fwith a view to profit without
OL,18,Fregistering as an upper tier waste
OL,19,Fcarrier.
