OL,7,FCCTV footage from Gravel Walks
OL,8,Fcaptures the moment a Ford Transit
OL,9,Fpickup arrived and tipped out the
OL,10,Fwaste before a male passenger covered
OL,11,Fit in petrol before it was set alight.
OL,13,FThe two other offences, which took
OL,14,Fplace at the former Forest Estate off
OL,15,FSouth Hetton Road Easington Lane were
OL,16,Falso recorded on CCTV.
