OL,7,FRoxby of Seventh Street, Blackhall
OL,8,FColliery, Hartlepool, was ordered to
OL,9,Fpay out a total of #1,935.70 including
OL,10,Fa victim surcharge of #114, clean-up
OL,11,Fcosts of #395 and costs of #1426.70
OL,13,FHe was also handed a 12-month
OL,14,Fcommunity order meaning he must
OL,15,Fcomplete 80 hours of unpaid work.
