OL,7,FThe Ford pickup was later seized by
OL,8,Fofficers from Sunderland City Council
OL,9,FEnvironmental Enforcement team,
OL,10,Fworking with police officers from
OL,11,FHetton's HALO Team (Hetton Aspirations
OL,12,FLinking Opportunities).
OL,14,FCouncillor Lindsey Leonard, Cabinet
OL,15,FMember for Environment, Transport and
OL,16,FNet Zero at Sunderland City Council,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Fly-tipping can be a real
OL,18,Fblight on our communities so I'm
OL,19,Freally pleased that we managed to
OL,20,Fachieve a successful prosecution in
OL,21,Fthis case.
