OL,5,Cestate
OL,7,F"The sheer audacity of this fly-
OL,8,Ftipping, dumping large amounts of
OL,9,Fwaste in broad daylight before setting
OL,10,Fit on fire has to be seen to be
OL,11,Fbelieved.
OL,13,F"I hope that the conviction and
OL,14,Fsentence, which requires this
OL,15,Findividual to do 80 hours unpaid work
OL,16,Fin the community, sends out a clear
OL,17,Fmessage that this type of anti-social
OL,18,Fbehaviour will not be tolerated under
OL,19,Fany circumstance.
