OL,5,Cestate
OL,7,F"The seizure of the van with the help
OL,8,Fof police working in the HALO Team is
OL,9,Falso evidence of the effectiveness of
OL,10,Fpartnership working in tackling issues
OL,11,Faffecting our communities, which is
OL,12,Fexactly what it was set up to do.
OL,14,F"I would urge anyone who comes across
OL,15,Ffly-tipping in their community to
OL,16,Freport it so that we can tackle it
OL,17,Fand, where the evidence is available,
OL,18,Ftake action against those responsible"
