OL,7,FA spokesperson for Northumbria Police
OL,8,Fsaid: "We understand and recognise the
OL,9,Fadverse impact that fly-tipping has.
OL,10,FIt can spoil the look and feel of our
OL,11,Fneighbourhoods.
OL,13,F"That's why we're proud to work
OL,14,Falongside Sunderland City Council and
OL,15,Four other partners as part of the HALO
OL,16,Fteam, and hope this conviction sends
OL,17,Fout a strong message to other would-be
OL,18,Foffenders."
